01:00:05,602 --> 01:00:10,064
<i>Little yellow canary</i>

448
01:00:14,277 --> 01:00:18,698
<i>Where will you sleep tonight?</i>

449
01:00:20,450 --> 01:00:23,369
<i>You can sleep</i>

450
