Dance, quick!

597
01:17:38,070 --> 01:17:38,904
Dance, quick!

598
01:17:40,822 --> 01:17:42,824
Don't you like this song?

599
01:17:42,908 --> 01:17:43,784
Sing it!

600
01:17:43,867 --> 01:17:45,994
Dance like this?

601
01:17:46,078 --> 01:17:49,414
<i>Poke and yank and poke and yank</i>

