673
01:32:55,528 --> 01:32:56,362
Ploy.

674
01:33:16,799 --> 01:33:17,633
Ploy.

675
01:33:18,467 --> 01:33:19,302
Ploy.

676
01:33:23,848 --> 01:33:24,682
Ploy!

677
01:33:27,310 --> 01:33:28,144
Ploy.

678
01:33:42,575 --> 01:33:43,409
Ploy.

679
01:33:45,578 --> 01:33:46,412
Ploy.

