683
01:37:04,902 --> 01:37:05,736
Ms. Joy?

684
01:37:08,280 --> 01:37:09,281
Aunt Joy.

685
01:37:12,368 --> 01:37:14,161
Let's get out of here.

686
01:37:20,459 --> 01:37:21,794
